Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:11.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,Moorgate Passage.\N{\rCHT}摩爾大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:22.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,Moorgate Passage.\N{\rCHT}摩爾大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:26.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,I see it over there!\N{\rCHT}在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:35.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,Bleeding rat-wags! What's gotten into them?\N{\rCHT}狗兒受到驚嚇 它們中了什麼邪啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:46.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,What in God's name is that?\N{\rCHT}老天 那是什麼怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:51.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,Halt!\N{\rCHT}停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,Halt!\N{\rCHT}停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:02.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Blimey! - Stop!\N{\rCHT}- 天哪 - 停
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:03.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Come on! - Halt!\N{\rCHT}- 快走 - 停
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:05.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,In the name of the law!\N{\rCHT}你已違反法令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:11.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Halt! - How the hell do we stop this thing?\N{\rCHT}- 停 - 要怎麼阻止這玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:13.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,I said, halt!\N{\rCHT}給我停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,Here.\N{\rCHT}它往金庫去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,Careful, mates. Careful.\N{\rCHT}各位 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,There's men inside!\N{\rCHT}裡面有人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,Please.\N{\rCHT}請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,Bring the scientist with us. Kill any who resist.\N{\rCHT}帶走科學家 反抗者一律處死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,Do we have him?\N{\rCHT}逮到他了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,Draper at your service, sir.\N{\rCHT}- 卡爾杜波 就在眼前 - 你要什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:19.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,The world, Herr Draper. I want the world.\N{\rCHT}世界 杜波博士 我要整個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,Really? That's so frightening.\N{\rCHT}真的？我好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,Don't wander off.\N{\rCHT}在這等著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,Where's Quatermain?\N{\rCHT}艾倫闊特曼在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:16.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,That gentleman at the back.\N{\rCHT}後面那位先生就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:32.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,Do I have the pleasure of addressing Allan Quatermain?\N{\rCHT}我是否有此榮幸與闊特曼相談？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:37.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do, sir. Indeed you do.\N{\rCHT}當然 你當然有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:39.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,You're not what I expected.\N{\rCHT}你跟我想的不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,I presume you're another traveler...\N{\rCHT}我想你是另一位下定決心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,...got it in your head to sample the Dark Continent.\N{\rCHT}來體驗黑暗大陸的旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:49.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,And while you're at it, hunt down old Allan Quatermain...\N{\rCHT}既然來了 你就來找獵人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,...and have him tell his adventures.\N{\rCHT}讓他跟你說說他的冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Well... - You just fill a seat, sir.\N{\rCHT}- 那麼…- 坐吧 坐下來讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:59.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,You can fill my glass. Bruce, double.\N{\rCHT}老布？來杯大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:07.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'll regale you with how I found King Solomon's Mines, or I could relate my...\N{\rCHT}就說我找所羅門王寶藏的歷程吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,It is not your past that interests me.\N{\rCHT}我感興趣的不是你的經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,My name is Sanderson Reed.\N{\rCHT}我叫桑德李得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:17.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,I am a representative of Her Majesty's British government.\N{\rCHT}我謹代表女王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:19.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,The empire needs you.\N{\rCHT}大英帝國需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,But the question is...\N{\rCHT}但問題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:24.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,...do I need the empire?\N{\rCHT}我需要大英帝國嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:27.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should toddle off. Should l, Allan?\N{\rCHT}我該退場了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:30.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course, Nigel, you toddle off.\N{\rCHT}當然 老奈 你退場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:31.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,Toddling.\N{\rCHT}退場囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:37.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nigel is useful for keeping the story seekers at bay.\N{\rCHT}老奈很會打發想聽故事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'm Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}我是闊特曼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,The empire is in peril.\N{\rCHT}英國正面臨危機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:49.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,You're probably too young to know, but the empire is always in some peril.\N{\rCHT}你可能還太年輕了 英國的危機一直都沒少過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:53.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,We need you to lead a team of unique men like yourself...\N{\rCHT}我們要你引領一隊特異奇兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,...to combat this threat.\N{\rCHT}像你一樣 解決此一威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,Regale me.\N{\rCHT}說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:05.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,There is great unrest, countries set at each other's throats, baying for blood.\N{\rCHT}情勢緊張 各國彼此敵對 火藥味十足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:09.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,The trouble of which I speak could set a match to the whole thing. War.\N{\rCHT}這樣的情勢 戰火一觸即發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,- With whom, exactly? - Everyone.\N{\rCHT}- 誰跟誰打？- 每個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,A world war.\N{\rCHT}世界大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:21.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,- That notion makes you sweat? - Heavens, man, doesn't it you?\N{\rCHT}- 那讓你冒汗？- 老天 難道你不會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,This is Africa, dear boy.\N{\rCHT}拜託 這裡是非洲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:26.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,Sweating is what we do.\N{\rCHT}流汗是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:30.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,Where is your sense of patriotism?\N{\rCHT}你的愛國心呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,God save the queen.\N{\rCHT}天佑女王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,- God save the queen. God bless her. - God save the queen.\N{\rCHT}- 天佑女王 - 天佑女王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,That's about as patriotic as it gets around here.\N{\rCHT}愛國心到這差不多就剩這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,But you're Allan Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}但你是獵人闊特曼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:46.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,Stories of your exploits have thrilled English boys for decades.\N{\rCHT}多年來你的故事振奮英國人民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:53.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,That I know, and Nigel has done a grand job reminding me.\N{\rCHT}我知道 老奈一天到晚都在提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:58.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,But with each past exploit...\N{\rCHT}但是每冒險一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:02.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,...l've lost friends. White men and black...\N{\rCHT}我就會失去朋友 黑人和白人皆有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,...and much more.\N{\rCHT}還有更多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:08.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,And I am not the man I once was.\N{\rCHT}我已不是昔日的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,The gentleman over there.\N{\rCHT}那邊那位先生就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,- We're in for the long haul. - Exactly.\N{\rCHT}- 我們在此等候已久 - 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:17.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Quatermain? - Why, yes indeed, sir.\N{\rCHT}- 闊特曼先生？- 正是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,Wrong Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}你殺錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,That's him.\N{\rCHT}是他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,Get down!\N{\rCHT}趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:35.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,- They're indestructible. - No, just armor-plated.\N{\rCHT}- 他們刀槍不入 - 不 只是穿了防彈甲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,Automatic rifles? Who in God's name has automatic rifles?\N{\rCHT}自動步槍？他們到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:55.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,That's unsporting. Probably Belgium.\N{\rCHT}真沒種 可能是比利時人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,Allan!\N{\rCHT}闊特曼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,Wicked waste.\N{\rCHT}真浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,Look out!\N{\rCHT}小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:07.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,Good old Britannia.\N{\rCHT}大不列顛萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there another one of these buggers?\N{\rCHT}還有一個癟三呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mr. Quatermain!\N{\rCHT}闊特曼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,Bruce, Matilda.\N{\rCHT}老布 瑪蒂達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:21.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,Our friend might have some information.\N{\rCHT}這位朋友可能會有線索
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:27.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,But he's so far away.\N{\rCHT}但是他跑很遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,Yes, I thought he was.\N{\rCHT}對 他跑很遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:35.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,God, I hate getting old.\N{\rCHT}年紀大就是不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:49.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Did you mean to just wound him? - Obviously.\N{\rCHT}- 你是故意只打傷他？- 當然囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:56.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,Stop him! I need information!\N{\rCHT}阻止他 我需要情報
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,Bloody poison.\N{\rCHT}該死的毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:10.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,You may have no love for the empire, but I know you love Africa.\N{\rCHT}你也許不愛英國 但我知道你愛非洲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:14.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,A war in Europe will spread to its colonies.\N{\rCHT}歐洲爆發戰爭必將禍延殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:28.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,It appears the war has arrived.\N{\rCHT}看來戰爭已經來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,very well, Reed...\N{\rCHT}好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,...l'm in.\N{\rCHT}我加入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,Excellent.\N{\rCHT}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,Pack for an English summer.\N{\rCHT}準備迎接英國夏日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,You made good time getting here.\N{\rCHT}你到的真快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:50.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,Not as good as Phileas Fogg, Around the World in 80 Days.\N{\rCHT}比不上菲利士環遊世界80天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:15.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,Where are we going, Australia?\N{\rCHT}我們要走去哪 澳洲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:26.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,And here we are, sir.\N{\rCHT}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,I don't like theatrics.\N{\rCHT}我不喜歡舞臺效果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:54.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,After Africa's veldts, London's weather isn't helping your mood, I see.\N{\rCHT}你從非洲草原來 倫敦的天氣似乎並不討你喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,Identify yourself.\N{\rCHT}請表明身分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:00.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'm known by many names, Mr. Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}我有很多身分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:04.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,My underlings call me sir. My superiors call me M.\N{\rCHT}我的屬下叫我〝先生“ 我的長官叫我〝M〞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,M?\NM？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,Just M.\N{\rCHT}就是M
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:14.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,I must say, the delight is mine, meeting so notable a recruit...\N{\rCHT}我得說我很榮幸 能會見如此出名的新成員…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:18.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,...to this newest generation of the League of Extraordinary Gentlemen.\N{\rCHT}加入天降奇兵小組
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,League of what?\N{\rCHT}什麼組？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:22.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,There have been other times when a danger upon the world...\N{\rCHT}當世界面臨危機時…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:26.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,...we required the services of singular individuals.\N{\rCHT}就需要能人異士效力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,How very curious.\N{\rCHT}真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:33.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,This museum is full of the curious.\N{\rCHT}這博物館裡有的是怪東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:36.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,Allan Quatermain, Captain Nemo.\N{\rCHT}闊特曼 這是尼莫船長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:39.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,I know of Mr. Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}我知道闊特曼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,And I know of you, captain.\N{\rCHT}我也知道你 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that you're a pirate.\N{\rCHT}謠傳你是海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:47.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer a less provocative title.\N{\rCHT}我喜歡比較正常的頭銜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,- I'm sure you would. - Gentlemen, please.\N{\rCHT}- 我想也是 - 各位別再客套了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nations are striking at nations.\N{\rCHT}國與國之間互相指控
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:56.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,Every attack marked by the use of highly advanced weaponry.\N{\rCHT}運用極先進的武器進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,These attacks are all the work of one man...\N{\rCHT}這些攻擊都是同一人所指使…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:04.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,...who calls himself the Fantom. - Very operatic. What's in it for him?\N{\rCHT}- 他自稱為魅影 - 他不會住歌劇院吧 他的動機何在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,Profit.\N{\rCHT}利益
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:11.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,Those machines are his creations, the work of scientists he holds imprisoned.\N{\rCHT}這些機器都是他所囚禁的科學家的發明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:15.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,His attacks have nations clamoring for the weapons that assail them.\N{\rCHT}他的攻擊讓各國爭相競購那些武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:19.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Then it's a race for arms. - And millions will perish.\N{\rCHT}- 軍備競賽 - 死傷將達數百萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:24.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,There's one last chance to avert war.\N{\rCHT}避免戰爭僅剩最後一絲契機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:28.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,The leaders of Europe are to meet secretly in venice.\N{\rCHT}歐洲領袖將在威尼斯秘密會商
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:32.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,And you believe that this Fantom will attack that conference?\N{\rCHT}而你認為這個魅影會破壞那場會議？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,If he can find it.\N{\rCHT}只要他找出地點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:38.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,We need a team to get to Venice stop him. This team consists of six members.\N{\rCHT}得有人阻止他 你們總共有6個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:42.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,- You'll have four days. - Four days to get to venice?\N{\rCHT}- 你有4天時間 - 4天要趕到威尼斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,- It's impossible. - Let me worry about that.\N{\rCHT}- 不可能 - 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well now, extraordinary gentlemen indeed.\N{\rCHT}還真是能人異士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:53.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,One of them is late.\N{\rCHT}有一位成員遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:57.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Harker, the chemist. - Oh, chemist guy?\N{\rCHT}- 哈克 化學家 - 化學家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,Do we get to blow something up then?\N{\rCHT}我們要轟掉什麼東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:04.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,My eyesight must be worse than I thought.\N{\rCHT}我的眼力退化的還真嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,No, your eyesight's fine.\N{\rCHT}你的眼力沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:13.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,No games, M.\N{\rCHT}別耍花樣 M
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:17.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,Some time ago, a talented, albeit misguided, man of science...\N{\rCHT}從前 有位天才娛入歧途的科學家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,...discovered the means to become invisible.\N{\rCHT}發現了隱形的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:25.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Yes, I recall the tale, but didn't he die? - Well, he did, but his process didn't.\N{\rCHT}- 我想起來了 他不是死了嗎？- 他是死了 但配方還在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:28.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,You see, I stole it, and here I stand for all to see.\N{\rCHT}我偷了它而現在我站在這
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:32.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Is this some parlor game? - Believe it.\N{\rCHT}- 這是在玩猜謎嗎？- 相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,Easy now, Allan.\N{\rCHT}放輕鬆 獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:39.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a bit of a draft in my nether regions.\N{\rCHT}我的屁股有點涼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:43.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,And I must say, it's quite refreshing.\N{\rCHT}我得說 這樣滿清爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:49.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce myself. Rodney Skinner, gentleman thief.\N{\rCHT}容我自我介紹 隱形人羅尼 小偷之王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:55.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,Now, I thought invisibility would be a boon to my work.\N{\rCHT}我以為隱形能讓我拓展事業
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:18:00.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well, you can imagine, it was my undoing.\N{\rCHT}你看得出來 剛剛我沒化妝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:04.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,Once you're invisible, it's bloody hard to turn back.\N{\rCHT}一旦隱形就很難恢復正常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,We finally caught him.\N{\rCHT}我們好不容易逮到了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:10.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,And they'll provide an antidote. Well, that's if I'm a good boy.\N{\rCHT}他們會給我解藥 只要我聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,And are you a good boy?\N{\rCHT}你聽話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:17.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,I guess you'll find out, won't you?\N{\rCHT}我想你會發現的 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,Am I late?\N{\rCHT}我遲到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,A woman's prerogative, Mrs. Harker.\N{\rCHT}女人的天性 哈克太太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:30.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,Please tell me this is Harker's wife with a sick note.\N{\rCHT}哈克太太是來幫先生請病假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:35.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,Sick would be a mild understatement. My husband's been dead for years.\N{\rCHT}說生病是客套 我先生早已過世多年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, Mrs. Wilhelmina Harker.\N{\rCHT}各位 威蜜娜哈克女士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:43.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mina's prior acquaintance with a reluctant League member...\N{\rCHT}她與之前一位不情願的組員互相熟識…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:46.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,...may prove useful. - I'm waiting to be impressed.\N{\rCHT}- 可能會有用 - 我等著開眼界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:50.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,The fate of the world is at stake. There are still two more members to recruit.\N{\rCHT}世界安全危在旦夕 還差兩位組員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:54.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,- The clock hands turn, gentlemen. - Kicking us out already?\N{\rCHT}- 各位 時間所剩不多 - 要走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:58.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,A moment ago, it was sherry and giggles.\N{\rCHT}不是才剛款待我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:15.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,- What in God's name is that? - I call it an automobile.\N{\rCHT}- 那是什麼玩意？- 我稱它為自動車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:17.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but what is it?\N{\rCHT}是啊 它到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,The future, gentlemen.\N{\rCHT}未來 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,The future.\N{\rCHT}未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:28.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,- This is my first mate. - Call me Ishmael. Please.\N{\rCHT}- 這是我的大副 - 請叫我乙石瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:01.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,So how did M get you?\N{\rCHT}說說看 M怎麼找到你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,None of your business.\N{\rCHT}不關你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,You're a little testy, Mr. Q.\N{\rCHT}你真愛生氣 歐吉桑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:13.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Harker, I doubt if you measure danger the way I do.\N{\rCHT}哈克太太 我懷疑你能像我一樣面對危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,And I imagine you with quite the library, Mr. Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}我想你滿會看相的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:20.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,All those books you must have read merely by looking at their covers.\N{\rCHT}這麼會以貌取人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:26.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,I've had women along on past exploits and found them to be, at best...\N{\rCHT}我跟女人一起冒過險 她們只會讓人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:29.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,...a distraction. - Do I distract you?\N{\rCHT}- 分心 - 我讓你分心了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:34.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,My dear girl, I've buried two wives and many lovers...\N{\rCHT}親愛的 我埋葬了2位妻子和許多情人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,...and I'm in no mood for more of either.\N{\rCHT}我沒興趣再玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:42.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,- You can send them my way... - Skinner, shut up.\N{\rCHT}- 你可以把她們讓給我…- 閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:28.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Shall I wait, captain? - No, bring my lady to me.\N{\rCHT}- 要不要等您？- 不用 去把我的寶貝帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:33.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,This is a charming spot.\N{\rCHT}這裡真豪華
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,Does Jack the Ripper live here?\N{\rCHT}傑克開膛手住這嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:50.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Good evening. - Mr. Dorian Gray?\N{\rCHT}- 晚安 - 不死人多利安？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:54.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,- I am indeed. - We came by way of M.\N{\rCHT}- 在下正是 - M吩咐我們來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:58.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,M for mystery.\N{\rCHT}神秘的M
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:03.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well, I've told him and I'm telling you, I'm not interested.\N{\rCHT}我跟他說過 也對你們說我沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:05.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,Dorian.\N{\rCHT}多利安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:11.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mina?\N{\rCHT}蜜娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.68,0:22:23.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,Charming décor.\N真炫的裝潢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:25.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,You're missing a picture, Mr. Gray.\N{\rCHT}有一幅畫不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:28.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,And you don't miss a thing, do you, Mr. Quatermain?\N{\rCHT}你真是觀察入微啊 不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.46,0:22:30.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,Oh, sometimes.\N{\rCHT}不儘然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:37.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,Scotch, anyone?\N{\rCHT}有人要喝威士卡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:39.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,Please, help yourself.\N{\rCHT}自己來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:42.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,Don't let it ruin your makeup.\N{\rCHT}別把妝弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:48.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed, Mr. Gray. You take Skinner's uniqueness in your stride.\N{\rCHT}這真令我訝異 你對隱形人似乎見怪不怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:53.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, I've seen too much in my life to shock easily.\N{\rCHT}我這輩子見過太多怪事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:58.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,Although, I must say I was surprised to see you again.\N{\rCHT}但我很訝異再見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:01.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well, our last parting was such sweet sorrow.\N{\rCHT}自從上次甜蜜又心傷的離別後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.33,0:23:05.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,So you're nothing more than an enticement.\N{\rCHT}所以你是個誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:09.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, your presence intrigues me.\N{\rCHT}然而 你的出現激起了我的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.50,0:23:14.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,They say you're indestructible, Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}傳聞你是不死之身 獵人闊特曼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.34,0:23:18.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well, a witch doctor did bless me once.\N{\rCHT}有位巫師庇佑過我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:21.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,I had saved his village.\N{\rCHT}我拯救了他的村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:26.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,He said Africa would never allow me to die.\N{\rCHT}他說非洲不會讓我死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:28.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,But you're not in Africa now.\N{\rCHT}但你現在不在非洲了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:30.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:35.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,I confess a curiosity as to what the files say about Mr. Gray.\N{\rCHT}我對多利安的檔案感到好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.69,0:23:39.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,We, all of us, have traits useful in this endeavor.\N{\rCHT}我們都各有所長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:44.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,A hunter, scientist, even Skinner has stealth.\N{\rCHT}獵人、科學家 連隱形人也有秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:47.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Cheers. - What have you?\N{\rCHT}- 乾杯 - 你有何專長？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.47,0:23:50.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,I have experience.\N{\rCHT}我經驗豐富
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:23:55.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,Gray and I have met before, many years ago at Eton College.\N{\rCHT}多利安和我以前見過面 多年前 在伊頓公校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:57.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,A lecture, no doubt.\N{\rCHT}想也知道 是去演講
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:02.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,You, the nation's hero, Dorian, the eager listening boy.\N{\rCHT}你是國家英雄 多利安則是乖巧的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.05,0:24:03.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,Quite the reverse.\N{\rCHT}剛好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:07.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,It was Gray visiting Eton...\N{\rCHT}是多利安造訪學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:10.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,...and I was the boy.\N{\rCHT}我才是那個乖學生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.07,0:24:19.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,What is it?\N{\rCHT}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.11,0:24:33.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Gray? - They are not mine.\N{\rCHT}- 多利安？- 不是我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:35.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,They're mine.\N{\rCHT}是我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.03,0:24:45.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,First meetings usually warrant introductions.\N{\rCHT}初次見面該自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.16,0:24:50.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,Of course. I am the Fantom.\N{\rCHT}當然 我就是魅影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.33,0:24:57.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,You are the League of so-called Extraordinary Gentlemen.\N{\rCHT}你們是奇兵小組
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.77,0:24:59.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,Introductions made.\N{\rCHT}介紹完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.74,0:25:05.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I'm scarred, Mr. Quatermain, not blind.\N{\rCHT}我臉上是有疤 獵人闊特曼 但我可沒瞎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.05,0:25:07.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,Drop the gun.\N{\rCHT}放下槍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.62,0:25:15.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,Your mission is to stop me. That, of course, I cannot permit.\N{\rCHT}你們的任務是要阻止我 當然 我可不准
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.46,0:25:19.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,So I give to you all a special one-time invitation.\N{\rCHT}所以我提出一次特別邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.50,0:25:21.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,Join me.\N{\rCHT}加入我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.07,0:25:25.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,You think we'll help start a war that will consume the planet?\N{\rCHT}然後發動戰爭摧毀世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.17,0:25:28.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,While you profit from your arms race?\N{\rCHT}還讓你海撈一票？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.14,0:25:33.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,I cannot deny that fortunes are made in war.\N{\rCHT}我無法否認戰爭可能致富
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.04,0:25:38.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,Imagine the riches a world war will yield.\N{\rCHT}想想世界戰爭能榨出多少財富
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.02,0:25:42.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,- He's not wrong. - Speak for yourself.\N{\rCHT}- 他說的沒錯 - 那是你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.75,0:26:52.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,Draw your pistol!\N{\rCHT}掏槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.06,0:26:55.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,I walk a different path.\N{\rCHT}我有自己的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.61,0:27:13.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,Run, James!\N{\rCHT}快逃 教授
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.99,0:27:27.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,Hang on.\N{\rCHT}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.80,0:27:36.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,Night-night.\N{\rCHT}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.16,0:28:02.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,Dorian!\N{\rCHT}多利安
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.11,0:28:20.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,What are you?\N{\rCHT}你到底是什麼怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.31,0:28:22.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'm complicated.\N{\rCHT}這很難解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.57,0:28:46.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,Damn.\N{\rCHT}該死
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.17,0:28:51.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,I thought I was special. You're invulnerable to harm.\N{\rCHT}我以為我很特別 你根本打不死嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.61,0:28:54.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,I don't like to boast. What happened to Mina?\N{\rCHT}我不喜歡自誇 蜜娜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.48,0:28:57.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's probably hip-deep in some sort of trouble.\N{\rCHT}也許惹了一屁股麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.78,0:29:01.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,Don't be such an alarmist, Mr. Q.\N{\rCHT}別這麼杞人憂天 歐吉桑
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.22,0:29:04.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,And my hips are none of your business.\N{\rCHT}也別老注意我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.53,0:29:09.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,Shoot!\N{\rCHT}開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.23,0:29:12.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,Go on!\N{\rCHT}開槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.13,0:29:20.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,I guessed as much, that they would do anything to protect you.\N{\rCHT}如我所料 他們會保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.07,0:29:24.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,See, now that's your biggest mistake.\N{\rCHT}你真是大錯特錯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.04,0:29:27.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,Thinking that I need them to protect me.\N{\rCHT}竟以為我需要他們保護
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.00,0:29:47.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,Extraordinary.\N{\rCHT}厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.00,0:29:53.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,Boy, they told me European women had funny ways.\N{\rCHT}他們都說歐洲女人與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.11,0:29:56.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,You missed a spot.\N{\rCHT}你沒清乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.34,0:30:01.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\N{\rCHT}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.11,0:30:04.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,And you are?\N{\rCHT}你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.15,0:30:07.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,Special Agent Sawyer of the American Secret Service.\N{\rCHT}特別探員索耶 隸屬於美國秘密情報局
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.02,0:30:10.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,Then America is aware of the situation?\N{\rCHT}美國也關心此事？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.42,0:30:14.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,If war starts in Europe, how long will it take until it crosses the Atlantic?\N{\rCHT}若歐洲爆發戰爭 過多久會跨過大西洋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.16,0:30:19.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,I followed you. I knocked out a straggler, and I took his place.\N{\rCHT}我跟蹤你們來的 我打昏一個槍手 取代了他
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.43,0:30:24.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,very noble. But this is a private party, and you're not invited.\N{\rCHT}真高貴的行為 但沒人邀你參加這場私人聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.84,0:30:28.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,Actually, Dorian has declined...\N{\rCHT}其實 多利安拒絕了我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.67,0:30:30.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,...so we are one shy of a full deck.\N{\rCHT}所以我們還欠一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.17,0:30:35.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, the battle was just the spur I needed.\N{\rCHT}剛好相反 這場打鬥激起了我的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.58,0:30:38.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,That and the thrill of a friendship renewed.\N{\rCHT}再加上重逢的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.85,0:30:43.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,So you're not needed.\N{\rCHT}所以就不需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.69,0:30:50.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Winchester. - That's right.\N{\rCHT}- 溫徹斯特製的 - 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.73,0:30:54.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,- It's modified, American style. - American-style shooting too.\N{\rCHT}- 我把它改成美國式的 - 槍法也很有美國風
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.30,0:30:57.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever it takes.\N{\rCHT}打得中最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.87,0:31:01.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,You like it, I brought two.\N{\rCHT}你若喜歡 我帶了2枝來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.87,0:31:06.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,You're in.\N{\rCHT}算你一份
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.75,0:31:13.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,- So, what's the next port of call? - Paris.\N{\rCHT}- 下一站去哪？- 巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.02,0:31:15.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,Just one last member to recruit.\N{\rCHT}還有一位成員要招募
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.72,0:31:19.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,Capture is more the word, and it will be quite a hunt.\N{\rCHT}用捕捉這個字比較恰當 準備打獵了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.02,0:31:22.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,You make him sound like some kind of animal.\N{\rCHT}你把他說的像只野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.49,0:31:27.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,Oh, speaking thus, Mrs. Harker, your conduct a moment ago...?\N{\rCHT}說到這點 你剛剛的行為呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.10,0:31:33.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,Indeed. We are all aquiver with curiosity.\N{\rCHT}沒錯 我們都很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.54,0:31:37.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well...\N{\rCHT}好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.44,0:31:43.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,My husband was Jonathan Harker.\N{\rCHT}先夫是強納森哈克
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.65,0:31:47.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,With a professor named van Helsing, we fought a dangerous evil.\N{\rCHT}我們跟隨凡赫辛教授力戰兇猛惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.45,0:31:53.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,It had a name, Dracula. He was Transylvanian.\N{\rCHT}它有個名字 塔古拉伯爵 特蘭夕法尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.52,0:31:55.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,European?\N{\rCHT}是歐洲人？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.46,0:31:59.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,One of those radicals the newspapers love to report on?\N{\rCHT}是報紙報導過的激進份子？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.60,0:32:02.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Mr. Skinner.\N{\rCHT}我不知道 隱形人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.17,0:32:10.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,Is the vampiric sucking of people's blood radical behavior?\N{\rCHT}吸人血的吸血龜算不算激進？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.05,0:32:21.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,Our transportation is forthcoming.\N{\rCHT}我們的交通工具來了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.15,0:32:23.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,A boat?\N{\rCHT}坐船？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.19,0:32:28.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,It travels on water, if that's what you mean.\N{\rCHT}算吧 它靠水行進
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.16,0:32:35.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,And beneath it.\N{\rCHT}也在水下航行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.22,0:33:00.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,Behold Nautilus, the Sword of the Ocean.\N{\rCHT}鸚鵡螺號 海中之王
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.53,0:33:06.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,Next stop, Paris.\N{\rCHT}下一站 巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.04,0:33:18.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,I don't see what we need a big monkey for.\N{\rCHT}我不懂我們要只大猴子有啥用
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.14,0:33:23.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well, this big monkey has terrorized the Rue Morgue for months.\N{\rCHT}這只大猴子搞得英國天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.61,0:33:27.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,Imagine the mayhem he'll give the enemy.\N{\rCHT}想想他能帶給敵人多少災難
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.66,0:33:35.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,- You missed! - I'm not trying to hit him.\N{\rCHT}- 你沒打中 - 我不想打中他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.56,0:33:39.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,Turn left, Mr. Hyde.\N{\rCHT}向左轉 海德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.34,0:33:49.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,Make him turn left, boy.\N{\rCHT}小子 逼他左轉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.31,0:33:56.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,If you can't do it with one bullet, don't do it at all.\N{\rCHT}槍法不准就別亂浪費子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.85,0:34:00.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,- He's doubled back. - Precisely. Come on.\N{\rCHT}- 他折返了 - 很好 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.06,0:34:06.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,Look out!\N{\rCHT}小心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.59,0:34:10.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,That was naughty.\N{\rCHT}真淘氣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.66,0:34:16.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Thanks. - Eyes open, boy.\N{\rCHT}- 謝了 - 照子放亮點
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.40,0:34:18.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,I can't protect you all the time.\N{\rCHT}我可沒辦法一直保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.51,0:34:24.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,He's afraid.\N{\rCHT}他害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.04,0:34:27.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,I can't smell anything.\N{\rCHT}我什麼都沒聞到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.14,0:35:01.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,Perfect.\N{\rCHT}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.71,0:35:04.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard, Mr. Hyde.\N{\rCHT}歡迎加入 海德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.06,0:35:17.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,"This hunt's too dangerous for a woman, even one such as you. Leave it to me."\N{\rCHT}〝這場獵捕女人不宜 你這麼猛的女人也一樣〞
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.30,0:35:26.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,Good God.\N{\rCHT}老天爺
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.41,0:35:37.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dorian.\N{\rCHT}你好 不死人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.08,0:35:41.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,The great white hunter's bagged his prize.\N{\rCHT}大獵人逮到獵物了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.19,0:35:45.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,Or the prize bagged him.\N{\rCHT}或是獵物逮到了他
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.19,0:35:52.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,Stay back, if you value your life.\N{\rCHT}退後點 愛惜自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.41,0:36:07.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,- You scratched me. - Better me than him.\N{\rCHT}- 你抓傷我了 - 總比被他抓到好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.51,0:36:12.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well, this is nice.\N{\rCHT}真夠猛的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.02,0:36:15.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hyde.\N{\rCHT}海德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.05,0:36:18.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,You've done terrible things in England.\N{\rCHT}你在英國犯下滔天大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.02,0:36:22.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,So terrible that you fled the country.\N{\rCHT}因此你逃離祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.73,0:36:27.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm ashamed to say that Her Majesty's government...\N{\rCHT}很遺憾的是女王陛下…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.33,0:36:31.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,...is willing to offer you amnesty...\N{\rCHT}決定給予你特赦待遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.57,0:36:34.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,...in return for your services.\N{\rCHT}只要你報效國家
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.17,0:36:38.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go home?\N{\rCHT}你想回家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.51,0:36:40.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,Home?\N{\rCHT}家？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.01,0:36:44.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,"Home's where the heart is," that's what they say.\N{\rCHT}俗語說〝家是每個人的避風港〞
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.65,0:36:47.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,And I have been missing London so.\N{\rCHT}我好想念倫敦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.68,0:36:52.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,Its sorrow is as sweet to me as a rare wine.\N{\rCHT}思鄉之情無以言喻
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.06,0:36:58.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,I am yours.\N{\rCHT}我加入你們
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.37,0:37:03.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid.\N{\rCHT}別害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.03,0:37:07.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Who says I'm afraid? - You do!\N{\rCHT}- 誰說我害怕的？- 你是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.47,0:37:09.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,You stink of fear!\N{\rCHT}你充滿恐懼的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.04,0:37:14.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,Quite the parlor trick.\N{\rCHT}這招挺炫的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.08,0:37:19.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,You wait till you see my next one.\N{\rCHT}等著看下一招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.30,0:38:11.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,Dr. Jekyll...\N{\rCHT}變身博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.27,0:38:13.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,...at your service.\N{\rCHT}等候指示
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.27,0:38:20.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,So...\N{\rCHT}好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.08,0:38:22.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,...the League is set.\N{\rCHT}團員到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.12,0:38:30.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,So is the date for the conference.\N{\rCHT}會議日期也定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.12,0:38:34.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,- We have three days. - Three days?\N{\rCHT}- 3天后 - 3天？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.66,0:38:37.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,Can this canoe do that?\N{\rCHT}這艘怪船行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.63,0:38:42.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,You underestimate the Nautilus, sir.\N{\rCHT}你低估鸚鵡螺了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.27,0:38:45.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,You underestimate her greatly.\N{\rCHT}你太小看她了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.03,0:39:16.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,She's out of your league.\N{\rCHT}她不是你碰得起的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.37,0:39:22.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mina?\N{\rCHT}蜜娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.17,0:39:28.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,Don't flatter yourself, Dorian.\N{\rCHT}別想的太美 多利安
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.31,0:39:33.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,Fortune rewards the bold.\N{\rCHT}勇夫必獲重賞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.02,0:39:41.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,If you require help during the voyage, Mrs. Harker, just let me know.\N{\rCHT}旅程中若有需要幫忙之處 請讓我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.52,0:39:45.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'm curious how you think you'll assist me, Agent Sawyer.\N{\rCHT}你認為可以幫我什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.66,0:39:48.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,Heavy lifting.\N{\rCHT}搬動重物
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.70,0:39:54.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,Light banter.\N{\rCHT}小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.17,0:39:58.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,- I'm a useful kind of guy. - You're sweet.\N{\rCHT}- 我是很有用的 - 你很貼心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.11,0:40:00.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,And you're young.\N{\rCHT}也很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.04,0:40:04.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,Neither are traits that I hold in high regard.\N{\rCHT}都不是我喜歡的特色
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.19,0:40:15.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,The solar panels are fully charged. We'll be diving in a moment.\N{\rCHT}太陽能板已經充電完畢 我們馬上就要下潛了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.19,0:40:18.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mr. Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}闊特曼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.36,0:40:21.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,Dr. Jekyll, Mr. Skinner.\N{\rCHT}變身博士、隱形人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.20,0:40:24.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Captain. - Nemo.\N{\rCHT}- 船長 - 尼莫船長
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.26,0:40:58.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,The plans the Fantom stole from the Bank of England. These are copies.\N{\rCHT}魅影從英國央行偷走的藍圖 這些是副本
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.14,0:41:02.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,Da vinci's blueprints of venice.\N{\rCHT}達文西的威尼斯藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.41,0:41:07.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,Its foundations...\N{\rCHT}它的地基…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.01,0:41:10.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,...and waterways.\N{\rCHT}還有水道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.11,0:41:14.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,So he'll attack the conference by sea.\N{\rCHT}所以他會從水路襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.77,0:41:34.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,Easy, Allan, easy.\N{\rCHT}別激動嘛 獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.54,0:41:39.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,Skinner! I want you dressed at all times!\N{\rCHT}隱形人 我要你隨時盛裝打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.61,0:41:43.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,Or it's my boot up your ass!\N{\rCHT}不然你就等著被我海扁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.35,0:41:53.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,Dinner is served, Mr. Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}晚餐準備好了 闊特曼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.06,0:41:56.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,I can offer you a jacket, if you require.\N{\rCHT}你若需要 我可以借你禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.33,0:41:58.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, no.\N{\rCHT}謝謝 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.29,0:42:03.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,But thank you for your contributions so far.\N{\rCHT}不過感謝你的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.70,0:42:09.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,I may have been overly rude earlier...\N{\rCHT}我先前太沒禮貌了…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.71,0:42:12.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,...when I called you a pirate.\N{\rCHT}竟然說你是海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.04,0:42:16.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,And I may have been overly charitable when I said I wasn't.\N{\rCHT}而我也許是抬舉自己 竟然說我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.81,0:42:19.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,But I try to live in the now...\N{\rCHT}我現在試圖…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.35,0:42:23.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,...where the ghosts of old wrongs do not abide. What of you?\N{\rCHT}擺脫昔日鬼魂的糾纏 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.55,0:42:26.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in ghosts, although I've seen my share.\N{\rCHT}我不信鬼 雖然我看過
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.02,0:42:29.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,Your past haunts you.\N{\rCHT}你的過去折磨著你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.70,0:42:36.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,vanity, pride...\N{\rCHT}虛榮、自尊…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.07,0:42:43.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,...mistakes that cost me someone dear.\N{\rCHT}令我失去了摯愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.04,0:42:46.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,So now you throw yourself in harm's way?\N{\rCHT}所以你現在放任自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.11,0:42:51.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,Old tigers, sensing the end, they're at their most fierce.\N{\rCHT}年邁的老虎 聞到死神的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.12,0:42:55.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,And they go down fighting.\N{\rCHT}反而勇猛異常
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.07,0:43:20.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,They're not how I left them, captain.\N{\rCHT}這裡之前不是這樣的 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.11,0:43:24.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,That's all I'm saying.\N{\rCHT}我只能這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.48,0:43:29.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,Powder?\N{\rCHT}粉末？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.45,0:43:32.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,You think sabotage?\N{\rCHT}有人在搞破壞？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.22,0:43:35.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,We ain't that far off course.\N{\rCHT}我們偏離航道不算太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.24,0:43:57.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,Did you want something?\N{\rCHT}你想幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.15,0:44:00.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,No, I was just wondering why you signed up for all this.\N{\rCHT}我在想你為何會答應加入
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.05,0:44:05.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo told me you hate the British Empire.\N{\rCHT}尼莫說你恨英國
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.12,0:44:07.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,They called, and I answered.\N{\rCHT}國家召喚 我欣然赴會
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.32,0:44:10.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well that ain't all of it, though, is it?\N{\rCHT}不全是那樣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.50,0:44:19.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,Sorry I asked.\N{\rCHT}抱歉我太多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.15,0:44:30.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,A few years ago...\N{\rCHT}幾年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.81,0:44:35.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,...the British approached me with a mission for queen and country.\N{\rCHT}英國找上我 女王和國家需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.18,0:44:38.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,That sounds like the morning ride to work for you.\N{\rCHT}對你而言這很平常
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.22,0:44:41.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,I signed on without hesitation.\N{\rCHT}我毫不猶豫就答應
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.52,0:44:44.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,I even took my son along.\N{\rCHT}還帶了我兒子同行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.19,0:44:49.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,I led and my son followed.\N{\rCHT}我領軍 他跟隨
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.20,0:44:53.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,He died in my arms.\N{\rCHT}他死在我懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.47,0:45:01.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,After that, I washed my hands of England and the empire and...\N{\rCHT}之後 我遠離英國…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.24,0:45:08.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,...the legend of Allan-bloody-Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}還有獵人闊特曼的一切傳奇
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.23,0:45:18.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,Now...\N{\rCHT}那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.20,0:45:21.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,...would you like to learn how to shoot?\N{\rCHT}想學學怎麼射擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.37,0:45:26.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,- I can already. - I saw, it was very American.\N{\rCHT}- 我已經會了 - 我看過 美式風格
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.17,0:45:31.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,Fire enough bullets and hope to hit the target.\N{\rCHT}你根本就是亂槍打鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.67,0:45:36.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,Sawyer, I'm talking about pipping the ace...\N{\rCHT}我說的是遠距離瞄準…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.05,0:45:38.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,...at 900 yards.\N{\rCHT}正中紅心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.02,0:45:42.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,Try.\N{\rCHT}試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.19,0:45:48.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy.\N{\rCHT}小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.60,0:45:58.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Aim. - That's easy.\N{\rCHT}- 瞄準 - 那很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.73,0:46:00.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,Allow for wind, target movement.\N{\rCHT}觀察標靶隨風向移動
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.04,0:46:04.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, that's easy too. - This is the part that's not.\N{\rCHT}- 那也很簡單 - 接著這部份可不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.71,0:46:07.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,You have to feel the shot.\N{\rCHT}你得感受射擊的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.54,0:46:09.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,Take your time with it.\N{\rCHT}慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.28,0:46:12.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,You have all the time you need.\N{\rCHT}你有的是時間
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.02,0:46:16.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,All the time in the world.\N{\rCHT}時間多的很
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.29,0:46:19.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,Take your...\N{\rCHT}慢慢…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.56,0:46:23.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,Too soon.\N{\rCHT}太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.56,0:46:27.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,But that was bloody close. And at 500 yards too.\N{\rCHT}但很接近了 距離也夠遠
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.13,0:46:29.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,Again.\N{\rCHT}再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.41,0:46:41.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,Did you teach your son to shoot like this?\N{\rCHT}你有這麼教過你兒子射擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.35,0:46:48.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,Quatermain?\N{\rCHT}闊特曼？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.03,0:47:31.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,That's Kali.\N{\rCHT}那是黑女神
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.46,0:47:34.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,Goddess of death.\N{\rCHT}死亡女神
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.13,0:47:39.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo worships death, can we trust him?\N{\rCHT}尼莫膜拜死亡 能信得過他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.54,0:47:44.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,He's not the one I'm worried about.\N{\rCHT}我所擔心的不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.00,0:48:08.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mina.\N{\rCHT}蜜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.03,0:48:13.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'm identifying a powder that Nemo found.\N{\rCHT}我在辨識尼莫找到的粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.17,0:48:17.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,Magnesium phosphorus.\N{\rCHT}鎂磷酸
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.04,0:48:21.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,Photographers use it to create a flash.\N{\rCHT}攝影家用它來製造閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.01,0:48:22.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,A camera, perhaps?\N{\rCHT}相機？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.54,0:48:26.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,It appears that someone wishes to capture this vessel's secrets.\N{\rCHT}看來有人想拍下這艘船的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.39,0:48:37.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,I was surprised you ultimately joined the League.\N{\rCHT}我很訝異你會加入
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.73,0:48:44.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,I mean to undo the flaws in my character.\N{\rCHT}我想改正我性格上的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.37,0:48:46.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,I want to face my demons.\N{\rCHT}我想面對我的心魔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.07,0:48:49.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,And what do you know of demons?\N{\rCHT}你對心魔瞭解多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.48,0:48:58.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,Do you recall a space on the wall of my home?\N{\rCHT}記得我家牆上有個空白的地方吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.75,0:49:01.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,A picture was missing.\N{\rCHT}有幅畫不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.05,0:49:04.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,Although the picture is my portrait...\N{\rCHT}雖然那是我的畫像…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.99,0:49:09.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,...I doubt you'd recognize the face upon it.\N{\rCHT}我懷疑你看到它還能認得出我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.63,0:49:14.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,Every year that passes, my portrait ages...\N{\rCHT}隨著歲月流逝 畫像逐漸變老…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.33,0:49:16.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,...instead of me.\N{\rCHT}我卻青春永駐
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.00,0:49:20.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,When did you last see it?\N{\rCHT}你上回看到它是何時？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.50,0:49:25.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,I dare not look upon it myself...\N{\rCHT}我不敢看它…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.47,0:49:29.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,...or the magic of the painting would be undone.\N{\rCHT}不然畫上的魔法就會解除
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.76,0:49:40.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nightcap?\N{\rCHT}睡前酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.36,0:49:44.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'm not much of a drinker.\N{\rCHT}我不愛喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.11,0:49:58.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,Just a small one then.\N{\rCHT}那就喝一小杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.81,0:50:07.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,How clumsy of me.\N{\rCHT}我真是笨手笨腳
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.65,0:50:10.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,We don't want blood everywhere.\N{\rCHT}我們可不想血濺四處
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.19,0:50:13.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Do we? - No.\N{\rCHT}- 對吧？- 對
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.06,0:50:15.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,Not blood.\N{\rCHT}不流血
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.63,0:50:25.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,Yes, Henry. Look, but don't touch.\N{\rCHT}對 亨利 看就好 別動手
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.54,0:50:28.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,That's your way.\N{\rCHT}那就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.81,0:50:32.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,Just shut up.\N{\rCHT}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.17,0:50:34.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,- I won't be tricked again. - Tricked?\N{\rCHT}- 我不會再上當了 - 上當？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.41,0:50:37.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,You've known what I was about each time you drank the formula.\N{\rCHT}你每回都是很清醒喝下藥的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.15,0:50:40.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,Liar! I'm a good man, a good man!\N{\rCHT}騙子 我是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.28,0:50:42.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well, who's lying now? You want it!\N{\rCHT}說謊的是誰？你想喝藥勝過想要她
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.19,0:50:46.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,Even more than you want her. You can't shut me out forever!\N{\rCHT}你沒法子讓我閉嘴的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.16,0:50:48.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Drink the elixir! - No!\N{\rCHT}- 快喝藥 - 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.66,0:50:51.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,- She barely even looks at you! - Be quiet!\N{\rCHT}- 她根本就懶得看你一眼 - 安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.53,0:50:54.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,She looked at me!\N{\rCHT}她看過我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.17,0:50:59.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,Contain your evil, doctor!\N{\rCHT}管好你的惡魔 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.17,0:51:04.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'll not have the brute free upon my ship.\N{\rCHT}我的船上可不容野獸撒野
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.57,0:51:06.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,Must I take drastic steps?\N{\rCHT}要我採取非常手段嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.41,0:51:09.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,- I am in control. - I very much doubt it.\N{\rCHT}- 一切在我掌控之中 - 我很懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.08,0:51:15.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,Your talk is all well and good, sir, but your own past is far from laudable.\N{\rCHT}你說的倒漂亮 但你輝煌的過去才令人懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.74,0:51:35.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,Let me out.\N{\rCHT}放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.61,0:51:43.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,If I didn't know better, I'd swear I already had.\N{\rCHT}我早知道我才是主宰
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.58,0:51:47.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,One of the vials is missing.\N{\rCHT}有瓶藥不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.35,0:51:50.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.\N{\rCHT}老天
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.15,0:51:56.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,So it's clear. With da vinci's blueprints and enough explosives...\N{\rCHT}很明白 有了達文西的藍圖 再加上足夠的炸藥…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.63,0:52:00.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,...he could set a bomb that would blow venice's foundations to rubble.\N{\rCHT}他可以把威尼斯的地基炸翻
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.06,0:52:05.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,- He's gonna sink the whole city. - Yes, and spark off his world war.\N{\rCHT}- 他要炸沉整個水都 - 沒錯 好引發他的世界大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.80,0:52:09.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that's not the sum of our problems.\N{\rCHT}恐怕我們的麻煩還不只這些
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.37,0:52:16.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,Skinner, he's taken a vial of my formula.\N{\rCHT}隱形人 他偷了一瓶我的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.25,0:52:20.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Are you sure? - Who else?\N{\rCHT}- 你確定？- 還會有誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.12,0:52:23.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,You've seen the way the sneaky blackguard operates.\N{\rCHT}你見識過他鬼祟的行徑了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.63,0:53:13.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,It's the carnival.\N{\rCHT}是嘉年華會
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.07,0:53:15.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,My God, we must locate that bomb.\N{\rCHT}老天 我們得找到炸彈才行
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.30,0:54:19.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,We can go no further, captain.\N{\rCHT}沒法再前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.57,0:54:21.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,All ahead, stop.\N{\rCHT}全部停止
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.83,0:54:48.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,Deploy the divers beneath the city.\N{\rCHT}派潛水夫潛到城下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.06,0:54:52.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,- The explosives must be found. - Aye, aye, sir.\N{\rCHT}- 一定要找到炸彈 - 是…長官
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.30,0:54:55.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,The city is vast. It could be anywhere.\N{\rCHT}這裡這麼大 它可能在任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.80,0:54:59.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,- What about Skinner? - I'd be alert for his treachery.\N{\rCHT}- 那隱形人呢？- 小心他偷襲
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.32,0:55:13.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,Bloody carnival.\N{\rCHT}該死的嘉年華
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.36,0:55:16.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,God, I feared the worst.\N{\rCHT}老天 我有很不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.09,0:55:17.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,It's all right. We still have...\N{\rCHT}不用擔心 我們仍…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.07,0:55:33.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,- The buildings are falling like dominoes! - We're too late!\N{\rCHT}- 建築物像骨牌般倒下了 - 我們太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.14,0:55:37.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,There must be more than one bomb.\N{\rCHT}炸彈一定不只一個
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.68,0:55:39.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo!\N{\rCHT}尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.68,0:55:43.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,The bombs are at the city's center. We must take out one key building.\N{\rCHT}炸彈在市中心 我們需要一棟關鍵建築
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.69,0:55:47.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Get ahead and destroy the next building! - Interrupt the chain!\N{\rCHT}- 搶在坍塌前摧毀下一棟建築 - 中止連鎖反應
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.29,0:55:51.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,With a beacon at the coordinates, I could launch a rocket and take out the domino.\N{\rCHT}只要有座標 我就能發射火箭彈摧毀它
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.13,0:55:55.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous! We'd never get there in time.\N{\rCHT}荒謬 我們不可能來得及的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.16,0:55:59.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,- No room for error, but it could work. - What are you talking about?\N{\rCHT}- 不能出錯 但絕對可行 - 你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.10,0:56:03.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,I'm an immortal, sir, not a gazelle. How can we outrun this?\N{\rCHT}我是不死人 不是蹬羚 怎麼可能跑得比這還快？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.68,0:56:12.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,Care for a spin?\N{\rCHT}來飆一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.25,0:56:17.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,Come on, Jekyll, get in!\N{\rCHT}變身博士 快上車
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.75,0:56:20.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,- I'll need coordinates. - Can you track this?\N{\rCHT}- 我需要座標 - 你能鎖定這車嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.26,0:56:22.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Of course. - Then this is the target.\N{\rCHT}- 當然行 - 這就是你的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.42,0:56:24.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Launch when you see the flare. - Right.\N{\rCHT}- 見信號就發射 - 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.66,0:56:28.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Jekyll, come on, we'll need Hyde. - No!\N{\rCHT}- 博士 快 我們需要海德 - 不
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.56,0:56:31.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,Hyde will never use me again.\N{\rCHT}海德不能再利用我了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.03,0:56:33.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,Then what good are you?\N{\rCHT}那你還有什麼屁用？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.42,0:56:48.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,Straight ahead, then turn left.\N{\rCHT}直走 再左轉
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.65,0:56:51.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,No, no, take a right after the canal ports.\N{\rCHT}不 過運河口右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.22,0:56:54.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,We must turn left to get ahead of the...\N{\rCHT}我們得左轉才能抄到前面…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.19,0:56:57.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,Snipers!\N{\rCHT}狙擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.06,0:57:02.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,Damn Skinner, he must have told them we were coming.\N{\rCHT}該死的隱形人 他一定先通知了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.21,0:57:20.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,Dorian!\N{\rCHT}多利安
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.42,0:57:27.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Can't get a clear shot! - Then take the wheel!\N{\rCHT}- 我無法瞄準 - 那就負責開車
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.39,0:57:30.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,Sawyer!\N{\rCHT}索耶
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.46,0:57:38.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,Sit down, you buffoon. I don't know how to drive this bloody thing!\N{\rCHT}坐下 你這個笨蛋 我不會開這玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.47,0:57:41.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,Get down!\N{\rCHT}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.30,0:57:43.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,Got it!\N{\rCHT}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.81,0:57:47.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,Save your bullets. These men are mine!\N{\rCHT}省點子彈吧 這些人是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.81,0:57:51.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?\N{\rCHT}你看到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.78,0:57:57.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Did you see what she just did? - Keep your eyes on the road!\N{\rCHT}- 你看到她的身手了？- 眼睛看路
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.99,0:58:07.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,It's a gauntlet!\N{\rCHT}是防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.76,0:58:11.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,The vampire lady has us covered!\N{\rCHT}吸血女在罩我們
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.33,0:58:47.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,The collapse has reached the carnival. Time's running out.\N{\rCHT}坍塌已抵達嘉年華會 沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.07,0:58:49.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,Tune the tracer to the car's frequency.\N{\rCHT}將追蹤器鎖定車子的頻道
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.40,0:58:52.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,- The rocket must be ready to launch. - Aye, aye, captain.\N{\rCHT}- 隨時準備發射火箭彈 - 是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.06,0:59:13.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sawyer, come on!\N{\rCHT}快啊 索耶 快
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.43,0:59:16.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Captain, we must pull out! - No, we stay and do our job!\N{\rCHT}- 船長 我們得撤退 - 不 我們留下克盡職責
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.01,0:59:26.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,Remember the flare. I'm off!\N{\rCHT}記得發信號 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.54,0:59:30.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,- What? - Don't forget, you're the target.\N{\rCHT}- 什麼？- 別忘了 你就是目標
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.14,0:59:57.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,- We'll be smashed apart! - Nemo says we stay, we stay.\N{\rCHT}- 我們會被壓扁的 - 船長說留下 就留下
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.58,1:00:08.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,He's overtaken the collapse! Be ready to launch!\N{\rCHT}他抄到坍塌前面了 準備發射
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.13,1:00:24.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,Launch!\N{\rCHT}發射
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.65,1:00:38.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,Bravo, boy.\N{\rCHT}幹的好 小子
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.67,1:01:04.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,He's done it.\N{\rCHT}他辦到了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.16,1:01:30.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,venice still stands.\N{\rCHT}威尼斯沒垮
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.17,1:01:39.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,You've failed.\N{\rCHT}你失敗了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.15,1:01:48.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,You see yourself as the brave John Bull.\N{\rCHT}你自以為是所向無敵的英國佬
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.09,1:01:53.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,But you're weak.\N{\rCHT}但你很孱弱
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.09,1:01:58.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,You run from the memory of your son's death.\N{\rCHT}你逃避兒子死去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.16,1:02:02.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,You should have trained him a little better.\N{\rCHT}你該把他訓練的強一些的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.17,1:02:10.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,You may as well have put the gun to his head and pulled the trigger yourself.\N{\rCHT}其實根本就是你害死他的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.08,1:02:17.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I know all about you.\N{\rCHT}沒錯 我瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.55,1:02:22.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,I know all about your spy.\N{\rCHT}我知道誰是你的眼線
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.72,1:02:24.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,Do you?\N{\rCHT}是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.06,1:02:31.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gray? What happened?\N{\rCHT}不死人？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.59,1:02:34.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,Misadventure. Have the others returned?\N{\rCHT}出了點差錯 其他人回來了？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.40,1:02:37.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,You're the first, hopefully not the last.\N{\rCHT}你是第一個 希望不是最後一個
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.07,1:02:41.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,That bastard, Skinner. A lot to answer for.\N{\rCHT}那個混帳隱形人得負全責
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.80,1:02:44.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,Skinner? No.\N{\rCHT}他？不對
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.14,1:02:46.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,Me.\N{\rCHT}是我
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.66,1:03:07.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,You?\N{\rCHT}是你？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.46,1:03:11.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,You don't know the half of it.\N{\rCHT}你根本沒搞清楚狀況
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.08,1:03:28.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,The Fantom is M.\N{\rCHT}M就是魅影
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.05,1:03:32.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,And the hunt is still on.\N{\rCHT}任務還沒完成
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.25,1:03:35.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,- What are you talking about? - The Fantom is M...\N{\rCHT}- 什麼意思？- 魅影就是M…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.06,1:03:37.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,...the man who recruited us. - Let me see that.\N{\rCHT}- 招募我們的人 - 但怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.69,1:03:40.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,- But how? - We'll get our answers.\N{\rCHT}- 但怎麼會？- 我們會查出來的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.80,1:03:44.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Where are the others? - Dorian's missing in action.\N{\rCHT}- 其他人呢？- 不死人在行動中走散了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.67,1:03:49.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Skinner must have fled when he realized we knew.\N{\rCHT}隱形人東窗事發後一定跑了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.44,1:03:53.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,And Sawyer?\N{\rCHT}索耶呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.31,1:03:56.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,He'll live to fight another day.\N{\rCHT}他隨時可以上場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.15,1:04:06.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I've had my fill of throats for this evening.\N{\rCHT}別擔心 我已經喝飽了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.36,1:04:11.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,Captain!\N{\rCHT}船長
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.37,1:04:22.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,It was Gray...\N{\rCHT}是不死人…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.17,1:04:24.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,...not Skinner.\N{\rCHT}不是隱形人
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.31,1:04:29.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,Gray has tricked us all.\N{\rCHT}不死人騙了我們
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.32,1:04:43.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,What is it?\N{\rCHT}什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.06,1:04:45.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,The sound of treachery!\N{\rCHT}叛徒的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.52,1:05:02.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?\N{\rCHT}那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.49,1:05:05.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,My exploration pod.\N{\rCHT}我的逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.55,1:05:27.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,- We could track it. - I intend to catch it!\N{\rCHT}- 我們可以追蹤它 - 我要奪回它
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.36,1:06:08.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,That is us.\N{\rCHT}那是我們
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.83,1:06:10.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,That is the Nautiloid.\N{\rCHT}那是鸚鵡子艇
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.20,1:06:13.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,We will be upon them soon.\N{\rCHT}很快就能追上他們了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.07,1:06:16.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,You okay?\N{\rCHT}你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.57,1:06:19.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,Just a little shaken.\N{\rCHT}只是有點訝異
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.21,1:06:31.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo?\N{\rCHT}尼莫？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.88,1:06:34.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,It's nothing of mine.\N{\rCHT}不是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.09,1:06:40.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,Captain, the noise came from this.\N{\rCHT}船長 聲音是從這傳出來的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.86,1:06:42.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,A recording disk?\N{\rCHT}錄音盤？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.47,1:06:53.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,Ready, professor?\N{\rCHT}準備好了 教授？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.27,1:06:56.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,Recording.\N{\rCHT}錄音
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.34,1:07:01.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, if you're hearing this...\N{\rCHT}各位 當你們聽到這個…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.25,1:07:05.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,...then every step leading up to it has gone as planned.\N{\rCHT}表示一切都按計劃進行
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.25,1:07:07.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,And I have been true to the goals set to me.\N{\rCHT}我也正朝我的目標邁進
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.05,1:07:09.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me, Dorian.\N{\rCHT}沒錯 是我 不死人
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.65,1:07:12.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,As you know by now, I'm no Ioyal son of the Empire.\N{\rCHT}你們現在知道 我不忠於英國
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.12,1:07:16.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,My Ioyalty to Mr. M comes in no small part from his possession...\N{\rCHT}事實上 我忠於M…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.66,1:07:19.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,...of something I hold very dear to my heart...\N{\rCHT}因為他握有我最珍視的東西…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.13,1:07:22.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,...something I would do anything to regain.\N{\rCHT}為取回它 我願付出一切
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.57,1:07:25.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Are you all right? - My ears hurt. It's nothing.\N{\rCHT}- 你還好吧？- 我耳朵痛 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.30,1:07:28.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,Everything so far has been misdirection.\N{\rCHT}目前為止 一切都被誤導了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.11,1:07:31.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,Sanderson Reed, the assassins in Kenya...\N{\rCHT}桑德、肯亞的刺客…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.11,1:07:35.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,...your recruitment and mission, the secret conference, a myth.\N{\rCHT}招募、任務、秘密會議、虛構的故事
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.15,1:07:39.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,Even the League itself. There is no League. There never was.\N{\rCHT}以及小組本身 沒有什麼小組 根本就沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.25,1:07:41.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,It was a ruse to get me closer to my goals.\N{\rCHT}那是我實踐目標的手段
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.09,1:07:44.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,He likes the sound of his own voice.\N{\rCHT}他真喜歡自己的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.26,1:07:47.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,You see, I want you, each of you, even tired old Ouatermain.\N{\rCHT}我要你們每一個人 就連老態龍鍾的闊特曼也是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.09,1:07:50.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,He'll capture Hyde where all others have failed.\N{\rCHT}因為只有他能捉到海德博士
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.66,1:07:53.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,The question is why. Why all this mask and mystery?\N{\rCHT}問題是為什麼 為何要裝神弄鬼？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.80,1:07:58.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,Because in the war to come, I intend to wield the greatest weapon of all:\N{\rCHT}因為在即將來臨的戰爭中 我要掌握最棒的武器：
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.54,1:08:00.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,The power of the League itself.\N{\rCHT}奇兵小組的力量
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.11,1:08:04.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,Turn it off, Henry. Please, turn it off.\N{\rCHT}快關掉它 拜託 關掉它
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.81,1:08:09.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,To that end, I set my wolf among you sheep...\N{\rCHT}為達目的 我在羊群裡放了只狼…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.05,1:08:10.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,Growl.\N{\rCHT}吼
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.51,1:08:13.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,...who'll gain your trust, quietly lead you astray.\N{\rCHT}取得你們的信任 令你們迷途
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.52,1:08:17.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,And all the while, I'll collect you, the parts of you I need.\N{\rCHT}順便擷取你們的長處
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.42,1:08:19.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo's science.\N{\rCHT}尼莫的科學
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.49,1:08:20.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,Magnesium phosphorus.\N{\rCHT}鎂磷酸
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.16,1:08:23.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,Skinner's skin sample.\N{\rCHT}隱形人的皮膚樣本
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.23,1:08:25.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,You scratched me.\N{\rCHT}你抓傷我了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.10,1:08:28.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,Jekyll's potion.\N{\rCHT}變身博士的變身藥
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.83,1:08:32.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,And Mina's blood.\N{\rCHT}吸血女的血
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.51,1:08:38.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,He's stolen us, and we let him.\N{\rCHT}他偷取我們 而我們毫無防備
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.14,1:08:41.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,If you fail to save venice, then I get my war.\N{\rCHT}你們若拯救失敗 威尼斯會爆發戰爭
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.58,1:08:43.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,And if you succeed...\N{\rCHT}但若拯救成功…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.48,1:08:47.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,...well, it's a small price to pay for Gray to go about his task.\N{\rCHT}不死人就得負責
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.35,1:08:50.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,War will come, sooner or later...\N{\rCHT}戰爭遲早總會爆發…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.35,1:08:52.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,...as inevitable as summer into autumn.\N{\rCHT}就像四季交替一樣無可避免
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.89,1:08:56.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,Now, some of you, perhaps Ouatermain if he isn't dead...\N{\rCHT}你們有些人 也許是獵人闊特曼 如果他還活著…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.59,1:08:59.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,...will pause to ask why I'm letting you know all this.\N{\rCHT}會問我為何要告訴你們這些
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.76,1:09:02.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,What fool reveals his stratagem before the game is over?\N{\rCHT}為何遊戲還沒結束就揭露謎底？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.34,1:09:07.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,It is over, for you...\N{\rCHT}遊戲結束了 對你們而言…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.47,1:09:10.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,...because my voice isn't the only sound being made.\N{\rCHT}這上面不只錄製了我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.57,1:09:15.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,While I've rambled on, a secondary layer of inaudible sound...\N{\rCHT}在聽我碎碎念之際 第二層無聲音波也在播放…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.85,1:09:20.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,...higher than humans can hear, audible to dogs and lower animals...\N{\rCHT}人類所聽不到 但狗和動物可聽到…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.08,1:09:25.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,...has been heard by crystal sensors dotted about your vessel.\N{\rCHT}且你們船上的水晶感應器會接收的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.76,1:09:29.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,Sensors attached to bombs.\N{\rCHT}感應器連結炸彈
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.73,1:09:32.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,"Bomb " voyage.\N{\rCHT}〝炸彈〞之旅
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.21,1:10:20.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!\N{\rCHT}快讓開
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.11,1:10:23.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,We have to surface!\N{\rCHT}我們得浮上水面
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.55,1:10:26.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,We're taking in water! Controls are not responding!\N{\rCHT}我們吃太多水 失去掌控
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.62,1:10:30.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,Primary engine room almost full! Aft bulkhead open. Pump valves jammed!\N{\rCHT}引擎室被淹沒了 幫浦的閥門卡
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.79,1:10:32.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Seal it off! - There are men in there!\N{\rCHT}- 封死它 - 裡面還有人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.16,1:10:36.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,For the greater good, we must seal it!\N{\rCHT}為了保全大家 必須封死它
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.30,1:10:49.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,We can do it, Henry.\N{\rCHT}我們做得到的 亨利
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.27,1:10:50.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\N{\rCHT}你胡說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.24,1:10:54.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,You know we can do it, together!\N{\rCHT}我們攜手合作就做的到
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.86,1:11:07.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,Seal it! Seal it up!\N{\rCHT}封起來 封死它
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.16,1:11:09.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,Wait!\N{\rCHT}等等
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.59,1:11:12.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,Don't close it!\N{\rCHT}別關
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.66,1:11:15.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing? - It's our last chance.\N{\rCHT}- 你幹嘛？- 這是我們最後一線生機
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.17,1:11:17.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,But I'm ordered to close it!\N{\rCHT}我奉命要把門封死
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.40,1:11:19.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,Then close it.\N{\rCHT}那就封吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.90,1:11:22.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,Seal it up.\N{\rCHT}把它封起來
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.55,1:12:40.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,Bravo, Edward. Bravo!\N{\rCHT}幹的好 大野獸
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.22,1:13:16.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,Let's not make a saint out of a sinner. Next time, he may not be so helpful.\N{\rCHT}別把野獸當英雄了 下回它也許幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.65,1:13:19.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,Can we still follow Gray?\N{\rCHT}我們還跟著不死人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.72,1:13:25.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well, we were the faster, but now we're the tortoise to his hare.\N{\rCHT}我們是變快了點 但跟他相比根本是龜速
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.13,1:13:28.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,- So we're done? - No, we're alive.\N{\rCHT}- 所以我們沒戲唱了？- 不 我們還活著
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.77,1:13:32.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,If M has any ideas to the contrary, that gives us an edge.\N{\rCHT}要是M沒料到 我們就有機會
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.67,1:13:35.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,We're getting a signal.\N{\rCHT}有訊號傳來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.48,1:13:39.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,Morse code.\N{\rCHT}摩斯密碼
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.81,1:13:42.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,- What's it say? - "Hello, my freaky darlings."\N{\rCHT}- 說些什麼？- 〝各位親愛的怪胎戰友〞
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.51,1:13:43.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,Skinner?\N{\rCHT}隱形人？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.11,1:13:48.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,"Hiding onboard little fish with Gray and M.\N{\rCHT}〝跟不死人與M同船
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.49,1:13:54.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,On way to base, east by northeast. Follow my lead."\N{\rCHT}前往基地 東偏東北 跟我來〞
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.75,1:14:50.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,Good work...\N{\rCHT}幹的好…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.21,1:14:52.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,...all of you.\N{\rCHT}各位
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.92,1:14:55.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,Captain?\N{\rCHT}船長？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.75,1:14:57.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,All ahead, full!\N{\rCHT}全速前進
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.20,1:15:15.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,If Skinner's headings are correct...\N{\rCHT}隱形人指引的方向若是正確…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.54,1:15:19.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,...we will pass through the treacherous Straits of Tartary...\N{\rCHT}我們會通過險峻的韃靼海峽…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.28,1:15:22.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,...and enter the Amur River, which empties out...\N{\rCHT}進入黑龍江
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.21,1:15:28.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,...into the frozen lakes of Mongolia, virtually inaccessible to outsiders.\N{\rCHT}直達蒙古的冰封湖泊 外人幾乎不可能進去
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.28,1:16:00.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,Peasant settlements.\N{\rCHT}鄉下地方
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.78,1:16:02.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,They're all deserted.\N{\rCHT}毫無人煙
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.65,1:16:05.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,Why deserted?\N{\rCHT}為什麼沒人？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.13,1:16:10.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,Fear, no doubt.\N{\rCHT}毫無疑問 因為恐懼
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.16,1:16:42.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,M's summer retreat.\N{\rCHT}M的避暑山莊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.63,1:16:45.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,This is where Skinner signaled he'd meet us.\N{\rCHT}隱形人要我們在這跟他會合
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.56,1:16:47.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,So we wait.\N{\rCHT}我們就等吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.52,1:17:14.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,Skinner?\N{\rCHT}隱形人？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.77,1:17:58.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,- We heard a noise. - It was nothing.\N{\rCHT}- 我們聽到聲音 - 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.24,1:18:09.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,Just an old tiger sensing his end.\N{\rCHT}只是只瀕死的年邁老虎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.55,1:18:13.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this was not his time to die after all.\N{\rCHT}也許它還不到該死的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.62,1:18:22.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,- I've been waiting all week to do that. - Get a grip, man.\N{\rCHT}- 我想這招想了整周 - 把持一下
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.39,1:18:24.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought I just did.\N{\rCHT}我不是才剛把了一把嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.13,1:18:27.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mina.\N{\rCHT}吸血女
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.10,1:18:31.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Report! - Well, hello to you too.\N{\rCHT}- 報告 - 你也好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.13,1:18:34.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,And need I remind you, I am naked in the snow.\N{\rCHT}拜託 我光著身子站雪地裡
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.67,1:18:40.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,I can't feel any of my extremities, and I mean any of them.\N{\rCHT}凸出來的地方都沒感覺了 尤其是最凸的小老弟
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.08,1:18:47.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,With all the suspicion on the ship...\N{\rCHT}大家都還懷疑我…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.12,1:18:49.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,...I knew you wouldn't believe I wasn't the spy.\N{\rCHT}我知道你們不會信我
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.22,1:18:52.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,I thought it was best to disappear.\N{\rCHT}我想我最好是消失
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.09,1:18:55.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,So, what are we dealing with?\N{\rCHT}我們面臨什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.13,1:18:57.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,The fortress is vast.\N{\rCHT}城寨很大
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.36,1:19:02.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,Furnaces produce iron for making M's weapons of destruction.\N{\rCHT}熔鐵爐煉製鋼鐵 製造M的武器
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.81,1:19:16.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,They're pieced together on the factory floor by a private army of ruthless men...\N{\rCHT}武器在工廠組裝 由一群他所養的…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.38,1:19:18.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,...who share his vision.\N{\rCHT}冷血的私人部隊執行
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.05,1:19:24.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,But the worst was to come.\N{\rCHT}但最糟的在後面
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.32,1:19:30.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,In the dry dock, M's best minds pervert Nemo's dream.\N{\rCHT}在幹船塢中 M的手下菁英 正在複製尼莫的心血
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.70,1:19:36.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,- The Nautilus? - Nautili. There's eight, for now.\N{\rCHT}- 鸚鵡螺號？- 是鸚鵡螺號們 有八艘
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.17,1:19:40.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,- What about the kidnapped scientists? - M holds their families hostage.\N{\rCHT}- 被綁架的科學家呢？- M以他們的家人為人質
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.17,1:19:44.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,The men work, or the women and children die.\N{\rCHT}不為他效力 妻兒就死路一條
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.18,1:19:47.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Monstrous! - That isn't the half of it.\N{\rCHT}- 混帳東西 - 還不只這些
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.88,1:19:52.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,The scientists are forced to work night and day to make new versions of us.\N{\rCHT}科學家們被迫日以繼夜複製我們的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.82,1:19:56.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,Invisible spies, an army of Hydes, vampiric assassins.\N{\rCHT}隱形間諜、野獸軍團、吸血刺客
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.19,1:20:00.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,M leaves for Europe today with a sample of the chemicals...\N{\rCHT}M今天要帶樣本去歐洲…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.49,1:20:03.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,...to sell to the most eager nation.\N{\rCHT}賣給最想要的國家
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.73,1:20:08.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,- I'll not let my evil infect the world. - Do you think any of us feel differently?\N{\rCHT}- 我不會讓我的邪惡影響世界 - 你以為我們沒有同感嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.33,1:20:10.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,Chimney pipes laced to buildings...\N{\rCHT}排煙管遍佈整棟建築…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.40,1:20:13.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,...and bombs in the furnaces would make quite a bang.\N{\rCHT}炸掉熔鐵爐可以瓦解一切
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.74,1:20:18.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,But someone needs to blow that place to hell, and I am least likely to be seen.\N{\rCHT}得有人把那地方轟掉才行 而我是最不易被人察覺的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.88,1:20:23.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,Skinner, I didn't know that you were such a bare-faced liar.\N{\rCHT}隱形人 你真會扯謊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.68,1:20:27.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,All that time pretending that you weren't a hero?\N{\rCHT}竟能一直假裝你不是英雄？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.28,1:20:29.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,Shut up, or I'll come to my senses.\N{\rCHT}閉嘴 不然我會展露本性的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.92,1:20:35.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,And besides, any more like me, and I'll lose the franchise.\N{\rCHT}何況 再多幾個我 我就不能賣加盟權了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.29,1:20:41.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,No, this cannot be a hunt to the death, more's the pity.\N{\rCHT}不 這回不能開殺戒 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.23,1:20:46.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,We must take M alive if his secrets are to be uncovered.\N{\rCHT}要揭露M的秘密 我們就得活捉他
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.40,1:20:48.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,Not Gray.\N{\rCHT}不死人可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.47,1:20:50.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,He's lived long enough.\N{\rCHT}他活的夠久了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.44,1:20:53.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Oh, I'll handle him. - No.\N{\rCHT}- 我來解決他 - 不用
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.28,1:20:58.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo, you and Hyde will free the prisoners.\N{\rCHT}尼莫 你跟海德去釋放人質
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.18,1:21:01.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,Sawyer and I will deal with M.\N{\rCHT}索耶和我去找M
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.22,1:21:03.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,Then the game is on.\N{\rCHT}遊戲開始了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.09,1:21:08.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,Do you mind?\N{\rCHT}不介意吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.59,1:21:12.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,Night-night.\N{\rCHT}祝你好夢
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.60,1:21:23.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,Your painting's in your room.\N{\rCHT}你的畫在你房裡
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.61,1:21:29.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,In return for the League, that was our deal, and I'm glad to see you honor it.\N{\rCHT}出賣奇兵小組 我們說好的 很高興你守信
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.15,1:21:30.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,So, what now?\N{\rCHT}你現在要幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.11,1:21:35.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,London. I've had my fill of violence. Now I'm in the mood for vice.\N{\rCHT}回倫敦 我冒夠險了 想放浪形骸一番
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.92,1:21:39.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,You could stay, share my dream.\N{\rCHT}你可以留下 與我共用美夢
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.16,1:21:46.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,I've lived long enough to see the future become history, professor.\N{\rCHT}我看盡許多未來步入歷史
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.53,1:21:51.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,Empires crumble. There are no exceptions.\N{\rCHT}帝國終會消失 沒有例外
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.43,1:21:53.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,You think you're better than me.\N{\rCHT}你以為你比我優秀
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.20,1:21:59.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,You forget, I've seen your painting.\N{\rCHT}你忘了 我看過你的畫像
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.67,1:23:00.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,Skinner said turn right at the column.\N{\rCHT}隱形人說柱子旁右轉
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.37,1:23:02.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,Oh, great. Which one?\N{\rCHT}妙啊 哪一根？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.91,1:23:06.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,This way.\N{\rCHT}這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.11,1:23:11.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,You lead, and I'll follow.\N{\rCHT}你領導 我跟隨
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.45,1:23:16.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,The scientists.\N{\rCHT}科學家們
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.35,1:23:18.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,They're for Nemo.\N{\rCHT}他們由尼莫負責
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.10,1:23:37.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,Prepare the armaments for shipment. Prepare the armaments for shipment.\N{\rCHT}準備運送武器…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.41,1:23:39.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,They're moving out.\N{\rCHT}他們要動身了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.38,1:23:41.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,Let's hope Skinner's up to the task.\N{\rCHT}希望隱形人能完成任務
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.78,1:23:43.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,You, help him out!\N{\rCHT}你 幫一下忙
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.14,1:24:13.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,Release them!\N{\rCHT}放了他們
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.68,1:24:15.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,Quietly!\N{\rCHT}安靜地
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.08,1:24:18.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,Get them back to the ship.\N{\rCHT}把他們帶回船上
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.12,1:25:00.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,Intruders! Intruders!\N{\rCHT}有人侵入…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.16,1:25:02.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,Intruders!\N{\rCHT}有人侵入
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.08,1:25:25.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,James, here's your box of tricks!\N{\rCHT}教授 這是你的魔法箱
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.15,1:25:31.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,The brute's potion, the vampire's blood...\N{\rCHT}變身藥、吸血龜的血…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.15,1:25:36.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,...the Indian's science and mounted samples of invisible skin.\N{\rCHT}海盜的科學 還有配好的隱形劑
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.16,1:25:38.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,They'll be all the rage in Europe.\N{\rCHT}它們會席捲全歐
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.36,1:25:40.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,The Nautiloid is fueled and ready.\N{\rCHT}鸚鵡螺號已準備好了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.17,1:25:47.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,- We have trouble. - Trouble? I call it sport.\N{\rCHT}- 我們有麻煩了 - 麻煩？我稱之為運動
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.87,1:25:52.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,Intruders! Indians! I think it's Captain Nemo and his men!\N{\rCHT}有人侵入  我想是尼莫船長和他的手下
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.84,1:25:54.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,The prisoners are escaping!\N{\rCHT}人質都逃走了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.71,1:25:57.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to kill these cretins?\N{\rCHT}這些白癡到底有幾條命啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.85,1:26:00.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Make this the last. - Damn them.\N{\rCHT}- 這回要徹底解決 - 該死的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.14,1:26:27.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo, get the scientists!\N{\rCHT}尼莫 快救走科學家
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.51,1:26:30.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've got?\N{\rCHT}你們就這麼點能耐？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.14,1:26:59.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,Do not move, M.\N{\rCHT}別動 M
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.11,1:27:07.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,Or would you prefer Professor James Moriarty?\N{\rCHT}還是該叫你莫理亞提教授？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.08,1:27:11.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,James Moriarty, the so-called Napoleon of crime?\N{\rCHT}莫理亞提教授 惡名昭彰的犯罪天才？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.19,1:27:17.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,That man died at Reichenbach Falls. He died, and I was reborn.\N{\rCHT}那個人死在萊亨巴哈瀑布了 他死了 而我重生
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.06,1:27:23.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,Watch out!\N{\rCHT}小心
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.60,1:27:26.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,Eyes open, boy. Can't protect you all of the time.\N{\rCHT}照子放亮點 我可沒法老護著你
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.79,1:27:46.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,Hello, lover.\N{\rCHT}你好啊 愛人
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.70,1:27:55.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,Mina.\N{\rCHT}蜜娜
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.50,1:27:59.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,You're alive.\N{\rCHT}你沒死
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.14,1:28:03.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,It's possible I can't die.\N{\rCHT}我也可能具有不死之身
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.54,1:28:08.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,The same could be said of you.\N{\rCHT}聽說你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.15,1:28:13.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,Let's put it to the test.\N{\rCHT}來測試一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.52,1:28:21.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,- Minx. - Do you realize what you've done?\N{\rCHT}- 女人 - 你知道你做了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.09,1:28:23.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,What you've let out of me?\N{\rCHT}你激發了我前所未有的情緒？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.73,1:28:26.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,A woman's wrath. Oh, I'm petrified!\N{\rCHT}發火的女人 我好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.17,1:28:37.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,We'll be at this all day.\N{\rCHT}我們這樣可以玩很久
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.19,1:28:55.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,The bedroom, Mina, does it give you memories or ideas?\N{\rCHT}臥室 這喚起你的記憶還是主意？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.22,1:28:56.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,Ideas.\N{\rCHT}主意
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.86,1:29:03.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,If that had been permanent, I'd have been very upset.\N{\rCHT}要是這會留下疤痕 我會抓狂
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.10,1:29:06.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,Your painting.\N{\rCHT}你的畫像
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.54,1:29:16.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,I hoped I'd get to nail you one more time.\N{\rCHT}我一直希望能再愛你入骨
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.08,1:29:19.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it'd be literally.\N{\rCHT}我沒想到會這麼入骨
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.23,1:29:36.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,Skinner?\N{\rCHT}隱形人？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.20,1:29:41.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's Skinner. What the hell are you doing here?\N{\rCHT}沒關係 是隱形人 你在這幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.80,1:29:44.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,What makes you think I'm Skinner?\N{\rCHT}你憑什麼以為我是他？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.71,1:30:52.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,Sawyer!\N{\rCHT}索耶
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.21,1:30:54.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,Run for it!\N{\rCHT}快跑
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.92,1:31:04.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,Keep moving!\N{\rCHT}繼續跑
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.49,1:31:07.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,Go over! Go, quickly!\N{\rCHT}快 快點
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.44,1:31:23.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,Come on! You want more?\N{\rCHT}來啊 你還想打嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.61,1:31:27.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,No!\N{\rCHT}不
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.18,1:31:33.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,Not the whole thing.\N{\rCHT}別整瓶灌下去
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.77,1:31:55.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,You are so lovely.\N{\rCHT}你真美
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.58,1:32:09.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.09,1:32:14.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,You broke my heart once.\N{\rCHT}你曾令我心碎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.16,1:32:17.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,This time you missed.\N{\rCHT}但這回你失手了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.89,1:32:21.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,You spoke once of wanting to meet your demon.\N{\rCHT}你說過要面對你的心魔
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.17,1:32:33.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,Here he is.\N{\rCHT}他在這
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.80,1:32:59.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,Skinner?\N{\rCHT}隱形人？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.14,1:33:05.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,That's the last time I play with matches.\N{\rCHT}我以後不敢玩火了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.80,1:33:31.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,End of the line, Moriarty.\N{\rCHT}你無路可退了 教授
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.81,1:33:43.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,To the death, but you'll need Hyde to make it mine.\N{\rCHT}要我死 你還需要野獸幫忙
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.18,1:33:46.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,He'll be making his own fun.\N{\rCHT}他現在正忙著呢
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.15,1:33:53.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo!\N{\rCHT}尼莫
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.16,1:33:59.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,Here!\N{\rCHT}這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.90,1:34:02.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo!\N{\rCHT}尼莫
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.34,1:34:12.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo, run!\N{\rCHT}尼莫 快逃
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.19,1:34:33.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?\N{\rCHT}那是什麼鬼東西？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.90,1:34:36.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,It's me on a bad day.\N{\rCHT}兩倍大的我
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.65,1:35:30.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,He's too strong. We're trapped.\N{\rCHT}他太強了 我們被困住了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.55,1:35:34.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,No, he's burning through the formula at an accelerated rate.\N{\rCHT}不 他的藥效在加速進行
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.13,1:35:40.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,He'll soon change back.\N{\rCHT}他很快就會打回原形
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.70,1:35:43.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,Nemo!\N{\rCHT}尼莫
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.82,1:36:02.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,I hope I've got your fire when I'm your age.\N{\rCHT}我真希望年老時能有你的身手
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.22,1:36:06.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,You will not live beyond today. That I promise you.\N{\rCHT}我保證你活不過今天
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.67,1:36:26.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,Hyde. Come on.\N{\rCHT}野獸 快跑
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.21,1:36:28.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,My formula's done.\N{\rCHT}我的藥效沒了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.73,1:36:50.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,Watch out!\N{\rCHT}小心
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.87,1:36:59.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,Think you'll come in here and wreck this? I'll rebuild it.\N{\rCHT}你以為能摧毀一切？我會重建
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.05,1:37:11.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,There'll be others like me, Quatermain.\N{\rCHT}會有其他跟我一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.79,1:37:14.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,You can't kill the future.\N{\rCHT}你無法扼殺未來
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.11,1:38:13.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,Do you ever get tired of being wrong?\N{\rCHT}你真是一錯再錯？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.75,1:38:17.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,The League, me, Skinner.\N{\rCHT}對於小組、我、隱形人
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.32,1:38:19.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,Wrong.\N{\rCHT}你都錯了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.79,1:38:22.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,Wrong about your little American friend as well.\N{\rCHT}你的美國朋友也一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.16,1:38:25.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,Do you really think he's ready for action?\N{\rCHT}你真以為他有本事？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.73,1:38:29.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,I think you've trained him about as well as you trained your son.\N{\rCHT}你訓練他就像訓練自己的兒子
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.37,1:39:06.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,Get him.\N{\rCHT}殺了他
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.84,1:39:14.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,- It's too far. - Take your time.\N{\rCHT}- 太遠了 - 慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.28,1:39:16.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,You're ready.\N{\rCHT}你行的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.35,1:39:25.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,Take your time.\N{\rCHT}慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.39,1:40:00.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,I got him.\N{\rCHT}我射中他了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.23,1:40:07.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,May this new century be yours, son...\N{\rCHT}願這新世紀屬於你 孩子…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.40,1:40:12.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,...as the old one was mine.\N{\rCHT}而舊世紀隨我而去
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.45,1:41:05.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,You remember he swore Africa wouldn't let him die?\N{\rCHT}記得他說過非洲不會讓他死吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.79,1:41:08.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,I wish the old boy had been right.\N{\rCHT}真希望老傢伙沒說錯
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.49,1:41:14.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,What's next?\N{\rCHT}接下來呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.80,1:41:16.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,I have long hidden away from the world.\N{\rCHT}我已隱於世外太久
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.20,1:41:22.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,Now I wish to see it anew as the century turns.\N{\rCHT}我希望能見證新世紀的到來
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.60,1:41:24.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,You're all welcome to join me.\N{\rCHT}歡迎你們加入我
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.51,1:41:28.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,We've all been hiding in one form or another.\N{\rCHT}我們多少也都跟你一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.91,1:41:33.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,The Nautilus awaits.\N{\rCHT}鸚鵡螺號在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.52,1:41:35.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,So who's coming?\N{\rCHT}誰要一起來？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.15,1:41:41.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,So long, old chap.\N{\rCHT}再見了 老戰友
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.86,1:41:44.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Allan.\N{\rCHT}再見了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.80,1:41:52.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.\N{\rCHT}再見
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.80,1:41:57.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,Thanks.\N{\rCHT}謝了

